Extension: BeUrgentCommunication

When there is a need to urgently communicate results of an order.

The official URL for this extension is: 

https://www.ehealth.fgov.be/standards/fhir/StructureDefinition/be-ext-urgent-communication

Status: draft
Extension maintained by: HL7 Belgium

Context of Use

This extension may be used on the following element(s):

  • ServiceRequest

Usage info

Usage:

  • Use this Extension: BeLabPrescription
  • Examples for this Extension: ServiceRequest/laboratory-order-example1

Formal Views of Extension Content

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots, and how the XML and JSON presentations work.

  • All
